<doc>
  <member name="D3D11_TEX2DMS_ARRAY_SRV">
    <summary>
      <para>Specifies the subresources from an array of multisampled 2D textures to use in a shader-resource view.</para>
    </summary>
    <remarks>
      <para>This structure is one member of a shader-resource-view description (see <see cref="D3D11_SHADER_RESOURCE_VIEW_DESC" />).</para>
    </remarks>
    <seealso href="https://docs.microsoft.com//windows/desktop/direct3d11/d3d11-graphics-reference-resource-structures">Resource Structures</seealso>
  </member>
  <member name="D3D11_TEX2DMS_ARRAY_SRV.FirstArraySlice">
    <summary>
      <para>Type: <b><a href="https://docs.microsoft.com//windows/desktop/WinProg/windows-data-types">UINT</a></b></para>
      <para>The index of the first texture to use in an array of textures.</para>
    </summary>
  </member>
  <member name="D3D11_TEX2DMS_ARRAY_SRV.ArraySize">
    <summary>
      <para>Type: <b><a href="https://docs.microsoft.com//windows/desktop/WinProg/windows-data-types">UINT</a></b></para>
      <para>Number of textures to use.</para>
    </summary>
  </member>
</doc>